univention-ucc-session-rdp (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * new ucr variables for xfreerdp (Bug #28986):
   - rdp/ignorecertificate to now ask for console based cert approval (Bug #28887)
   - rdp/geometry to set a desired resolution (Bug #28986)
   - rdp/clienthostname to manually set a hostname (Bug #28986)
  * default values for rdp/ignorecertificate and rdp/checknla is true to 
    enable out-of-the-box w2k8 connections
